he Surface that Anandtech tested. </p> <p>The Micron SSD posted speeds of 400 megabytes-per-second when reading data &#8230; <a href="/8301-10805_3-57568209-75/microsoft-surface-pro-shows-off-its-inner-ultrabook/" class="readMore">Read more</a></p> <footer> <div class="postByline"> <div id="nameAndTime"> <!--[if lt IE 9]> <noscript><div class="timeTag datestamp"></noscript> <![endif]--> <time class="datestamp"> February 7, 2013 6:06 PM PST </time> <!--[if lt IE 9]> <noscript></div></noscript> <![endif]--> <span class="author"> By <a rel="author" href="http://www.cnet.com/profile/mbrookec/">Brooke Crothers</a> </span> </div> </div> <div section="tags" class="tagsWrap"> <div class="postLinks"> <dl> <dt class="pipe"><b>Tags:</b></dt> <dd> <a href="/8300-5_3-0.html?keyword=ipad+4">iPad 4</a>, </dd> <dd> <a href="/8300-5_3-0.html?keyword=ipad">iPad</a>, </dd> <dd> <a href="/8300-5_3-0.html?keyword=c400">C400</a>, </dd> <dd> <a href="/8300-5_3-0.html?keyword=ipad+3">iPad 3</a>, </dd> <dd> <a href="/8300-5_3-0.html?keyword=surface+pro">Surface Pro</a>, </dd> <dd> <a href="/8300-5_3-0.html?keyword=microsoft+surface">Microsoft Surface</a>, </dd> <dd> <a href="/8300-5_3-0.html?keyword=micron">Micron</a>, </dd>  <dd> <a href="/8300-5_3-0.html?keyword=apple">Apple</a>, </dd> <dd> <a href="/8300-5_3-0.html?keyword=ssd">SSD</a>, </dd> <dd> <a href="/8300-5_3-0.html?keyword=windows+8">Windows 8</a>, </dd> <dd> <a href="/8300-5_3-0.html?keyword=flash+memory">flash memory</a>, </dd> <dd> <a href="/8300-5_3-0.html?keyword=windows+8+pro">Windows 8 Pro</a>, </dd> <dd> <a href="/8300-5_3-0.html?keyword=solid-state+drive">solid-state drive</a>, </dd> <dd> <a href="/8300-5_3-0.html?keyword=micron+technology">Micron Technology</a> </dd> <!-- Added DVAR tag per bug 422649. liaHeader value=iPad 4;iPad;C400;iPad 3;Surface Pro; --> </dl> </div> </div> </footer> </div><!-- /post --> </article> <!--[if lt IE 9]> <noscript></div></noscript> <![endif]--> <div class="nrelateUnit" id="nrelate_relate